setup:-
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Config: 

used to set db paramaters

location

/config.php

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

templates: 

location for your html template files

/templates

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

templates config: 

used to configure your template

location

/templates/templates.xml

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Symlinks (required): 

symlinks that are required by the cms in order to work correctly

(/core/core/lib) mvcms -> ../../mvcms

~#: cd /path/to/site/root/core/core/lib
~#: ln -s ../../mvcms mvcms

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

useful locations:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
bootstrap app: 
/core/core.php

librarys: 
/core/core/lib

Zend library: 
/core/core/lib/Zend